Package core.action_strategies

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActionStrategy
    Interface for different strategies which that allows for handling BehaviourState to call for the actual action
    ActionStrategyFactory
    Factory interface for creating different ActionStrategy implementations
    BidirectionalHandler
    Handles the lateral and longitudinal maneuverability of the unit, based on what ActionStrategy has to handle each axis.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionStrategyFactoryImpl
    Factory for creating different ActionStrategy instances
    BidirectionalHandlerImpl
    Handler class for handling control in X-axis and Y-axis
    EmgyStop
    ActionStrategy for handling emergency stops when immediate action needs to be taken
    LateralController
    Lateral controlling class for handling lateral automation
    PIDParser
    An ActionStrategy which parses the sensor data of a dedicated Sensor
    RemoteController
    An ActionStrategy that handles the incoming navigational requests from a remote controller in a specific axis.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    RemoteController.Axis
    The filter used to filter out unwanted data
